definition: Suizhong county in Huludao 葫蘆島|葫芦岛, Liaoning
to hit (the mark)/to be hit by/to suffer/to win (a prize, a lottery)

sentences.english: Taking Suizhong County of Liaoning Province as an example, the evaluation results were analyzed.
